    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seedborne Soldiers is an auto battler roguelike presented in the sweet, nostalgic style of a low-polygon 90s game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039930/extras/1b53dec1e342c59a12248e8b7073ac3d.poster.avif?t=1771903480\" width=1170 height=672 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039930/extras/1b53dec1e342c59a12248e8b7073ac3d.webm?t=1771903480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039930/extras/1b53dec1e342c59a12248e8b7073ac3d.mp4?t=1771903480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Draft a team</strong> from a pool of 75 (!) characters pulled from across the cosmos, and fight to escape dangerous Dreamworld. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix and match from a huge selection of <strong>Traits, Trinkets, and upgradeable Equipment </strong>to capitalize on powerful synergies and overcome unique enemies and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039930/extras/c91306634776accfcc2f984415e3dd5d.poster.avif?t=1771903480\" width=1170 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039930/extras/c91306634776accfcc2f984415e3dd5d.webm?t=1771903480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039930/extras/c91306634776accfcc2f984415e3dd5d.mp4?t=1771903480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pick your battles and plan your path with care.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each round, choose a fight based on its difficulty and rewards. You can survive a few losses, but too many mean game over. Should you chase the loot to build your dream team, or just try to survive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039930/extras/c685060b0a0c69e7c8b2fea8a98dce2e.poster.avif?t=1771903480\" width=1170 height=672 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039930/extras/c685060b0a0c69e7c8b2fea8a98dce2e.webm?t=1771903480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039930/extras/c685060b0a0c69e7c8b2fea8a98dce2e.mp4?t=1771903480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Our favorite auto battlers + our favorite roguelikes = Seedborne Soldiers </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Field units with matching traits to power up your team</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect 3 copies of a unit to combine them into a level 2 (9 total copies make a level 3)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Draft 5 tiers of units; higher tiers are more powerful but rarer and costlier </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade equipment and collect trinkets to maximize your team’s potential</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquer 3 Maps filled with 30+ enemies (plus a variety of non-combat encounters), each capped by a deadly boss</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Each character has a unique Spell, and many have an additional unique Effect.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039930/extras/0713d62df22c6ffe3f48d6d2d7916ea6.avif?t=1771903480\" width=1184 height=888 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use the map to navigate away from bad RNG into broken combos. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Peek at the Traits of upcoming units, collect items which help find matches, and utilize the Harvest system at Shelters to shore up your team. The map system is designed to give you agency to pursue your build without sacrificing those glorious highroll moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Double-casting Sages, loot-loving Nobles, or item-wary Ascetics… Dreamworld is your oyster! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Good luck, summoner!</h2>",
